    "Title": "Anybody Seen ~mission(TargetName)?",
    "DisplayTitle": "Anybody Seen [TargetName]?",
    "Description": "I know better than to send someone like ~mission(TargetName) out by themselves, but that didn\u2019t stop me from being a fool and doing it. Now the dumb SOB hasn\u2019t returned my comms and nobody has set eyes on them in a few days.\n\nIf you got the time, I could use someone to go over to ~mission(Location|Address) and see if they\u2019re still there. You get paid even if they wind up being dead.\n\n-Stows",
